@startuml
!define RECTANGLE class

title Remarks System - Deployment and Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Chrome Extension\n(popup.html/record.js)" as Extension
participant "Deno Deploy\n(Serverless Platform)" as Deploy
participant "Web Server\n(server.ts)" as Server
participant "Handler Layer" as Handler
participant "homePage.jsx" as HomePage
participant "remarks.ts" as RemarksHandler
participant "quotes.ts" as QuotesHandler
participant "tripPage.jsx" as TripPage
participant "queryFauna.ts\n(Data Access)" as QueryFauna
database "FaunaDB\n(GraphQL API)" as FaunaDB
participant "GitPress Blog\n(RSS Feed)" as GitPress

== Extension Deployment Flow ==
User -> Extension: Install Chrome Extension
activate Extension
Extension -> Extension: Load popup.html\nLoad popup.css\nInitialize record.js
deactivate Extension

== Server Deployment Flow ==
Deploy -> Server: Deploy server.ts to Deno Deploy
activate Server
Server -> Server: Initialize sift router\nLoad environment variables\n(FAUNA_SECRET)
Server -> Handler: Register route handlers
activate Handler
Handler -> HomePage: Register / route
Handler -> RemarksHandler: Register /remarks route
Handler -> QuotesHandler: Register /quotes route
Handler -> TripPage: Register /trip route
deactivate Handler
deactivate Server

== User Creates Remark (Control Flow) ==
User -> Extension: Click meeting type button
activate Extension
Extension -> Server: POST /remarks\n(Remark data)
activate Server
Server -> RemarksHandler: Handle POST request
activate RemarksHandler
RemarksHandler -> QueryFauna: queryFauna(createRemarkMutation)
activate QueryFauna
QueryFauna -> FaunaDB: GraphQL Mutation\n(Create Remark)\nAuthentication: FAUNA_SECRET
activate FaunaDB
FaunaDB -> FaunaDB: Store remark data
FaunaDB --> QueryFauna: Mutation response
deactivate FaunaDB
QueryFauna --> RemarksHandler: Success/Error
deactivate QueryFauna
RemarksHandler --> Server: Response
deactivate RemarksHandler
Server --> Extension: HTTP Response\n(mode: no-cors)
deactivate Server
Extension --> User: Feedback
deactivate Extension

== User Views Homepage (Control Flow) ==
User -> Server: GET /
activate Server
Server -> HomePage: Handle GET request
activate HomePage
HomePage -> QueryFauna: queryFauna(getTotalRemarksQuery)
activate QueryFauna
QueryFauna -> FaunaDB: GraphQL Query\n(Count Remarks)\nAuthentication: FAUNA_SECRET
activate FaunaDB
FaunaDB --> QueryFauna: Total count
deactivate FaunaDB
QueryFauna --> HomePage: Remarks count
deactivate QueryFauna
HomePage -> QueryFauna: queryFauna(getRemarksQuery)
activate QueryFauna
QueryFauna -> FaunaDB: GraphQL Query\n(Fetch Recent Remarks)\nAuthentication: FAUNA_SECRET
activate FaunaDB
FaunaDB --> QueryFauna: Remarks list
deactivate FaunaDB
QueryFauna --> HomePage: Remarks data
deactivate QueryFauna
HomePage -> HomePage: Render JSX\n(Format timestamps)
HomePage --> Server: HTML response
deactivate HomePage
Server --> User: Display homepage\n(Count + Remarks list)
deactivate Server

== User Creates Quote (Control Flow) ==
User -> Server: POST /quotes\n(Quote data)
activate Server
Server -> QuotesHandler: Handle POST request
activate QuotesHandler
QuotesHandler -> QueryFauna: queryFauna(createQuoteMutation)
activate QueryFauna
QueryFauna -> FaunaDB: GraphQL Mutation\n(Create Quote)\nAuthentication: FAUNA_SECRET
activate FaunaDB
FaunaDB -> FaunaDB: Store quote data
FaunaDB --> QueryFauna: Mutation response
deactivate FaunaDB
QueryFauna --> QuotesHandler: Success/Error
deactivate QueryFauna
QuotesHandler --> Server: Response
deactivate QuotesHandler
Server --> User: HTTP Response
deactivate Server

== User Views Travelogue (Control Flow) ==
User -> Server: GET /trip
activate Server
Server -> TripPage: Handle GET request
activate TripPage
TripPage -> GitPress: Fetch RSS feed\n(HTTP Request)
activate GitPress
GitPress --> TripPage: RSS XML data
deactivate GitPress
TripPage -> TripPage: Parse RSS feed\nRender JSX with entries
TripPage --> Server: HTML response
deactivate TripPage
Server --> User: Display travelogue page
deactivate Server

== Error Handling Flow ==
User -> Server: Request to any endpoint
activate Server
Server -> Handler: Route request
activate Handler
Handler -> QueryFauna: queryFauna(GraphQL operation)
activate QueryFauna
QueryFauna -> FaunaDB: GraphQL Request
activate FaunaDB
FaunaDB --> QueryFauna: Error response
deactivate FaunaDB
QueryFauna -> QueryFauna: Handle error\nLog error details
QueryFauna --> Handler: Error object
deactivate QueryFauna
Handler --> Server: Error response
deactivate Handler
Server --> User: HTTP Error\n(Status code + message)
deactivate Server

@enduml
